description: Demolition of existing buildings and erection of 983 residential units, together with a 4,430sqm hotel (Use Class C1), 1,845sqm of retail/commercial floorspace (Use Class A1), 1,230sqm of retail/commercial floorspace (Use Class A2-A5), 5,495sqm of community floorspace (Use Class D1), a 2,810sqm supermarket (Use Class A1), a 217sqm station, a public square, publicly accessible open space and associated access, car parking, cycle parking, landscaping and servicing.
